flowchart TD
    Request[/HTTP GET /admin/customer<br/>params: bpNo, userId/] --> Controller[AdminController.getCustomer]
    Controller --> LogStart[Log: getCustomerDetails Start]
    LogStart --> ServiceCall[adminService.getCustomer<br/>bpNo, userId]
    ServiceCall --> ValidateParams{bpNo and userId<br/>present?}
    ValidateParams -->|missing| Err400[/400 Bad Request/]
    ValidateParams -->|present| SAPCall[SAP API<br/>CUSTOMER_PROFILE_RETRIEVAL<br/>/CustomerProfileRetrieval]
    SAPCall --> SAPResult{SAP response<br/>status?}
    SAPResult -->|error| MapError{Error type?}
    MapError -->|not found| Err404[/404 Not Found/]
    MapError -->|upstream failure| Err502[/502 Bad Gateway/]
    MapError -->|other| Err500[/500 Internal Server Error/]
    SAPResult -->|success| CustomerType{Customer type?}
    CustomerType -->|EBS| EBSPath[Use EBS_CUSTOMER_DETAILS_RETRIEVAL<br/>/CustomerDetailsRetrieval]
    CustomerType -->|MSSL| MSSLPath[Use MSSL_CUSTOMER_DETAILS_RETRIEVAL<br/>/MSSLCustomerDetailsRetrieval]
    EBSPath --> SAPDetails[(External: SAP Backend)]
    MSSLPath --> SAPDetails
    SAPDetails --> SubscriptionLookup[Retrieve subscription preferences]
    SubscriptionLookup --> HasSubscription{Subscription<br/>found?}
    HasSubscription -->|yes| MergeSubs[Merge subscription data<br/>into customer profile]
    HasSubscription -->|no| SkipSubs[Skip subscription merge]
    MergeSubs --> MaskingStep[Apply MaskingUtil<br/>to sensitive fields]
    SkipSubs --> MaskingStep
    MaskingStep --> BuildResponse[Build GetCustomerResponse DTO]
    BuildResponse --> Resp200[/200 JSON GetCustomerResponse/]
